</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>&lt;dependency&gt;
</span><span class='line'>      &lt;groupId&gt;org.mybatis&lt;/groupId&gt;
</span><span class='line'>      &lt;artifactId&gt;mybatis&lt;/artifactId&gt;
